    <body>
      <section eId="sec_18_1820">
        <num>18-1820</num>
        <heading>Establishment of a commission for village manager</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_18_1820__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the number of members of\nsuch commission, which shall not exceed seven and of which number more\nthan one-half shall not be members of the board of trustees,</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_18_1820__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the\ncompensation, if any, of the members of the commission,</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_18_1820__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the\nemployment of staff or consultants, if any, and</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_18_1820__subsec_d">
          <num>(d)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the date by which\nsuch commission shall report its recommendations to the board, which\ndate shall be no later than two years after the final appointment of all\nmembers of the commission. The appointment of members of the commission,\nand the filling of any vacancies on such commission, shall be made as\nprovided in this chapter.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
